Class Party

java.lang.Object
Party
All Implemented Interfaces:
IRepresentative
public class Party extends Object implements IRepresentative
The Party class creates Party objects that represent political parties in a CPL election. It implements IRepresentative, which creates the outline for a representative.
Author:
Garrett
